<p>Hello, <%= @user.email %>!</p>

<p>We received a request to permanently delete your account.</p>

<p>Your confirmation code is:</p>

<p style="font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:4px"><%= @code %></p>

<p>Enter this code on the deletion confirmation screen. It expires in 30 minutes.</p>

<p>If you did not request account deletion, ignore this email — your account will not be deleted unless you complete the confirmation.</p>
